    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不是你典型的怪物收集游戏！</h2><br>嘿！你喜欢遗物吗？我知道你喜欢...我们超爱遗物。在《Niknaks》中，你的遗物就是你的队伍！你的Niknaks不仅仅在战斗中有效，场外也会有影响！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038530/extras/1173e7cc926c5b12538c63378eddf486.poster.avif?t=1760121114\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038530/extras/1173e7cc926c5b12538c63378eddf486.webm?t=1760121114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038530/extras/1173e7cc926c5b12538c63378eddf486.mp4?t=1760121114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造 <strong>疯狂的</strong> 连招</h2>•每次游戏开始时选择你的<strong><u>神祇</u></strong><br>•调整你的手牌顺序以触发强大的效果<br>•选择能够相互协同的Niknaks，打造最强团队<br>•将Niknaks叠加在一起，构建强大的组合<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038530/extras/be68e50ca3076385ae24fb3c2d46e173.poster.avif?t=1760121114\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038530/extras/be68e50ca3076385ae24fb3c2d46e173.webm?t=1760121114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038530/extras/be68e50ca3076385ae24fb3c2d46e173.mp4?t=1760121114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>•<strong>每场战斗后</strong>，你将有机会选择新的<strong>队友</strong>和其他<strong><strong>升级</strong></strong>！<br><br>•多个区域，每个区域都有其独特的主题、奖励和敌人。<br><br>游戏开发过程中未使用任何AI技术。",
